Class OpenHistoryquoteQueryStrategy

java.lang.Object
grafioschtrader.gtnet.handler.impl.historyquote.BaseHistoryquoteQueryStrategy
grafioschtrader.gtnet.handler.impl.historyquote.OpenHistoryquoteQueryStrategy
All Implemented Interfaces:
HistoryquoteQueryStrategy
@Component public class OpenHistoryquoteQueryStrategy extends BaseHistoryquoteQueryStrategy
Strategy for AC_OPEN mode: queries local Security/Currencypair historyquote data only. Behavior:
  • Queries local Security and Currencypair entities to find matching instruments
  • Uses batch queries with 10-day threshold optimization for efficient data retrieval
  • Filters results by sendableIds - only sends data for allowed instruments
  • Returns local historical data that matches the request
  • For instruments where no data is available AND the server WANTS to receive data, returns a "want to receive" marker with the date from which data is desired
  • Does NOT interact with GTNetHistoryquote table
Unlike AC_PUSH_OPEN, this mode only shares data from instruments that exist in the local database, and must consider sendableIds to filter what can be exchanged.
